      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey im planning a solo trip to chicago next month. i'm looking for a neighborhood that feels pretty safe, upscale, and has a good sense of community. also, given the current social climate lately, are there any specific areas i should just avoid so i don't run into any trouble?",
